      "raw_text": "A committee has been appointed\nby the trades council to ascertain\nhow many business Arms are hand\nling the goods of j. M. Ward & Co.\nThe garment workers of Peoria, ILL.,.\nhave been out on strike against this\nconcern since December 20 The COM\nmittee will urge Spokane business\nmen to cease patronizing the goods\nmade by Ward & Co."
